  <brief_title>Study to Compare a Fast Gama Camera for Nuclear Imaging to Conventional Camera</brief_title>
  <acronym>GP_D-Spect</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Multi Purpose D-spect Camera for General Nuclear Scans</official_title>
